<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset='UTF-8'>
	<title>{{subject}}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; background-color: #fffae6;">
	<div class="container" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); background-image: url('https://www.example.com/vintage-paper.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center;">
		<h1 style="color: #7c2900; font-size: 30px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 2px solid #7c2900;">안녕하세요, {{name}}님!</h1>
		<p class="subheading" style="color: #7c2900; font-size: 18px; margin: 0;">{{currentDate}}에 보낸 편지가 도착했습니다.</p>

		<div class="content" style="margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0 10px; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; text-decoration: underline;">
			{{{text}}}
		</div>

		<div class="signature" style="text-align: right; font-size: 16px; font-style: italic; margin-top: 30px; color: #7c2900; text-decoration: underline;">
			<p>오늘도 주님과 동행하는 하루가 되기를...</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
